	<h2 >Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

						<header class="centralized">
							<img src="<%= asset_path "divider.png" %>" class="divider img-responsive img-center">
						</header>

	<div class="panel-group" id="accordion">

		<div class= "question-general">
			<h3>General Questions</h3>
			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">What is VoiceGems?</a></h4>
				</div><!-- END PANEL-HEADING -->
				<div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						VoiceGems is a cloud-based service that allows DJs to connect wedding couples with their guests in a new and meaningful way.
						VoiceGems collects short pre-recorded wedding messages/toasts for DJs to download and blend into their entertainment mix.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo"> How does VoiceGems work? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						First, create a VoiceGems Event Page (just enter a title and date). Then share a custom link for that page with anyone you choose: guests, family and friends.  Clicking the link takes them to our easy-to-use online voice-recorder where they create a short meaningful message/toast. These messages are available on your personal VoiceGems Page,
						where DJs can download and blend them into their music/entertainment on the day of the event, providing an unparalleled experience.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree"> How do I get VoiceGems and how much does it cost? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						<strong>Couples</strong> can purchase a personal VoiceGems Page <a href="<%= newcustomer_couple_path %>" target="_blank">here</a>. Service for one event (one VoiceGems Page) is $99.  Just invite your DJ to use the page in the 'Admin' tab on your page (simply enter their email address).

						<br/><br/>

						<strong>DJ's</strong> can <a href="<%= newcustomer_trial_path %>" target="_blank">sign up</a>, purchase bundles of VoiceGems Pages at a bulk discount, and then set up the pages for clients at a fair fee-for-service. 
						
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSixteen"> How do I give my DJ access to the recordings?</a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseSixteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Simply add your DJ as an admin from the Admin tab on your VoiceGems page (just enter their email address.)
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwelve"> Is my payment information secure? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseTwelve" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Yes. If fact, our entire site uses up-to-date SSL Encryption (indicated by the padlock icon and https:// prefix in your browser's address bar).
						This means that not only payment information, but all user information, is securely handled.
						As an added layer of security, we use the Stripe payment gateway, and strictly comply with their payment processing protocol.
						This means that encrypted payment information (such as credit card numbers) never touch our database,
						but are instead immediately transmitted to Stripe's industry-standard secure processing system.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->


			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFourteen"> What is the refund policy/guarantee?</a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseFourteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Our service may be unique, but we strive to make sure it's the best it can be.  We offer a 100% Money-Back Satisfaction Guarantee.  Just email info@voicegems.com<br/>
						<br/>
						<strong>Couples:</strong> if you are not satisfied with VoiceGems for any reason, just send a refund request within 30 days after your event, and we will process a full refund within 7 days. <br/><br/>
						<strong>DJ's:</strong> if you are not satisfied with VoiceGems for any reason, just send a refund request within 30 days of purchase, and we will process a full refund within 7 days. <br/><br/>
						We should that we have not yet ever received a single refund request - everyone loves mixing music with meaning!
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour"> What events does VoiceGems support? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						VoiceGems can be used for any event where you want to Mix Music With Meaning.
						This includes weddings, corporate events, graduation and retirement parties, and anniversary celebrations,
						birthdays, bar-mitzvahs and bat-mitzvahs, and so much more!
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFive"> How many messages/toasts can be recorded and what's the duration of each messages? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						An unlimited number of messages/toast can be recorded for each event.
						To keep those messages meaningful and easy to integrate, each one is limited to 30 seconds by default (think Twitter for audio!).  To request a larger message maximum time-length for your event's messages, simply contact us below and our customer service will be happy to accommdate!
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSix"> Is personal info sold to any third parties? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Never. We keep all user information, including names, emails, and any other personal information, strictly confidential.
						Email addresses may be used for VoiceGems related communication,
						but is not given to any third party.  Please see our <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path %>.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSeven"> Are all the guests supposed to be invited to record VoiceGems? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseSeven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						VoiceGems gives you the power to decide who you want to participate in this special experience.
						Once a VoiceGems Page is created, the recording link can be sent to any number of people you choose.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEight"> How long does my VoiceGems page last? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseEight" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Forever. VoiceGems are meant to create a lasting memory for couples.
						VoiceGems are securely stored on the cloud, so not only do they make the event even more special on the big day, but VoiceGems can be cherished for a lifetime.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->



			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseNine"> Does VoiceGems work on all devices? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseNine" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Yes. As long as there's a mic, a user can record a VoiceGem via laptop, desktop, or mobile web.
						We should note that while possible on mobile devices,
						managing VoiceGems Event Pages (creating a VoiceGems Event Page, previewing VoiceGems, downloading MP3's, adding another 'Admin' for a VoiceGems Event Page)
						is optimized for non-mobile devices.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTen"> How does VoiceGems ensure recording quality? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseTen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						VoiceGems is now fully integrated with Auphonic's cutting-edge cloud-based audio processing system.
						Every recording is automatically treated with Noise, Hiss, and Hum Reduction algorithms, as well as Global Loudness
						Normalization and True Peak Limiter, to ensure that every VoiceGem is polished to the highest-possible quality. Learn more <a href="<%= auphonic_path %>" target="_blank">here</a>.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->
		</div>

		<div class="questions-DJ">
			<h3>DJ Questions</h3>

			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEleven"> If I purchase more than one event page, do I get any discount? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseEleven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						Yes! VoiceGems Event Pages purchased in bulk receive discounts. DJ's, <a href="<%= newcustomer_trial_path %>" target="_blank">sign up</a> for more information.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->


			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-heading">
					<h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThirteen"> Is there any registration or cancellation fee? </a></h4>
				</div>
				<div id="collapseThirteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
					<div class="panel-body">
						No. Registering for VoiceGems allows you to create Event Pages and gives you access to special promotions.
						Payment is on a per-event basis.
					</div><!-- END PANEL-BODY -->
				</div><!-- END COLLAPSE-ONE -->
			</div><!-- END PANEL-DEFALT-->

		</div><!-- END QUESTIONS-DJ -->

	</div><!-- END PANEL-GROUP -->

